<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 10 Apr 2026 19:24:14 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>新旧交融</title><link>https://some.pics/69d94e5bdfc6a</link><description>&lt;p&gt;旧物新事&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="An old branch of an apple tree, covered in lichen, on which some new moss is beginning to form and a tiny apple blossom bud sits" height="3000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/roteskuffen/69d94e5bdfc6a.jpg" width="3000"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://roteskuffen.some.pics"&gt;@roteskuffen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Apr 2026 19:24:14 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>贝尔赫姆站</title><link>https://some.pics/69d90baf30d06</link><description>&lt;p&gt;大约17公里后：贝尔赫姆站&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Na ongeveer 17km: Berchem Station" height="3000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/simondh/69d90baf30d06.jpg" width="4000"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://simondh.some.pics"&gt;@simondh&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Apr 2026 14:39:46 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>春天</title><link>https://some.pics/69d909d661b0e</link><description>&lt;p&gt;春天&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="De Lente" height="3000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/simondh/69d909d661b0e.jpg" width="2998"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://simondh.some.pics"&gt;@simondh&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Apr 2026 14:31:53 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>银行运钞车</title><link>https://some.pics/69d9000e12222</link><description>&lt;p&gt;草皮银行&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Bank van gras" height="3000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/simondh/69d9000e12222.jpg" width="4000"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://simondh.some.pics"&gt;@simondh&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Apr 2026 13:50:11 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>暮色天鹅游湖</title><link>https://some.pics/69d8fed9022d0</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一只孤独的天鹅在黄昏时分滑过广阔湖面的轻柔涟漪。天鹅以侧影被捕捉，它修长的脖颈弯曲着，向左游去。背景中，一道绵长倾斜的山脉暗影坐落在苍白清澈的天空下，落日的柔和余晖在地平线上徘徊。前景的水面幽暗，细小的波纹赋予其质感，映照着天空柔和的光线。这幅图像采用了低曝光、冷色调的调色，带有深靛蓝色的阴影，以及沿着地平线饱和度降低的淡橙色高光。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A lone swan glides across the gentle ripples of a vast lake at dusk. The swan is captured in profile, its long neck curved as it swims toward the left. In the background, the dark silhouette of a long, sloping mountain range sits beneath a pale, clear sky, with the soft glow of a setting sun lingering on the horizon. The water in the foreground is dark and textured with small waves, reflecting the muted light of the sky. The image uses a low-exposure, cool-toned grade with deep indigo shadows and a desaturated, pale orange highlight along the horizon." height="2343" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/mangochutney/69d8fed9022d0.jpg" width="1757"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://mangochutney.some.pics"&gt;@mangochutney&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 Apr 2026 13:45:00 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>